                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                            </head>
                            <p>On September 25, 1951, the Secretaries of State and Defense submitted
                                to the National Security Council the First Quarterly Progress Report
                                on <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 48/5. Several sections of
                                this report deal with United States policy toward Japan. For text,
                                see <ref target="#pg_80">page 80</ref>.</p>
